   <p>For an account of the American occupation of Plowed Hill on the night of 26 Aug., see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0270&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-01-02-0270-fn-0006#GEWN-03-01-02-0270-fn-0006" class="document">GW to Richard Henry Lee, 29 Aug. 1775, n.6</a>.</p>

</div>
